# E4: keep the docker build context clean. examples/docker/Dockerfile is
# built from the repo root and COPYs `packages ./packages`; without this
# file the host's node_modules (platform-specific native bindings!), stale
# dist output, and repo junk all leak into the build context and image.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/*.tsbuildinfo
.git
tmp
documentation/.vitepress/cache
documentation/.vitepress/dist
benchmarks/.datasets
**/.DS_Store
